{"tid":712606,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"著名數學撚系列：古典城邦的改革者","createTime":"2018-06-22T08:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T09:03:58.000Z","uid":187216,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"916f98c99073c57b7c13f376999b3da095e390b3","tid":712606,"uid":187216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>古典城邦的改革者(1)</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n諗極都唔明點解以前啲人咁撚鍾意搞革命，郁啲就話改革，郁啲就話維新。現代解釋：冇醫療福利、冇社會保障，唔係俾人充軍塞外就係流放邊疆，有閪計呀？(編按：慘得過我哋依家)<br />\n呢個系列第二期會介紹一位中世紀嘅改革撚，不過開始之前我要攞嚿石頭嚟講。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/math.ucr.edu/home/baez/YBC7289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fmath.ucr.edu%2Fhome%2Fbaez%2FYBC7289.jpg&h=6e076fb1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n呢嚿石頭，犀利嘞，係一塊有成3700幾年歷史嘅碎石板。仲啟發咗個數學撚寫一部FF《石頭記》，嗰個故事開頭係咁講嘅：「戰神」馬爾杜克手握釘頭錘、張弓搭箭擊殺「大地之母」迪亞馬特，然後將佢支解。佢嘅身體一半化為天，另一半化為地，原本戴响胸前嘅「命運石板」(Tablet of Destiny)爆裂成無數碎石散落人間。<br />\n千百年後，一鳩一撚拎住刻有天界印記嘅石板碎片離開美索不達米亞平原，出走地中海，同時將六十進制嘅秘密帶進沿岸區域......<br />\n<br />\n等等，六十進制？咩撚嘢六十進制啊？<br />\n你哋時時刻刻都用緊，仲要問？六十秒一分鐘，六十分鐘一個鐘；再唔係問吓啲術數撚咩叫六十年一個甲子囉。<br />\n等等，咩撚嘢秘密？咪爛鬼碎石板一塊！<br />\n嗱，千祈唔好睇小嗰啲曆法、公式、演算法則呀，响啲撚樣手上嘅話，小則發財致富，大則傾國傾城架！唔信？想當年，唔係波蘭班數學撚破解咗&rdquo;Enigma&rdquo;密碼機，盟軍同納粹德軍，鹿死誰手真係尚未可知。講貼身啲，叫顧鳴高教授些牙條方程式嚟玩吓，啲連登仔就唔駛咁撚灰啦。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160227/photo/bkn-20160227033008154-0227_00822_001_01p.jpg?20160227063923\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160227%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160227033008154-0227_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20160227063923&h=e86623ec&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n講番塊石板，上面記載嘅算式响嗰陣時絕對係研究生/博士生程度，讀唔明點撚樣起金字塔同空中花園！唔係你以為自己玩緊Civilization，㩒個掣就起好。<br />\n响進位制同埋數字系統都未成熟嘅古巴比倫，3700幾年前班數學撚能夠用六十進制算出開方2嘅近似值，簡直係痴鳩線嘅成就。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Ybc7289-bw.jpg/300px-Ybc7289-bw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F0%2F0b%2FYbc7289-bw.jpg%2F300px-Ybc7289-bw.jpg&h=a6505a12&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n得嘞，我都知你班大帝睇唔明啦！畫埋出腸，拆解埋個金手指密碼：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/6b9faf0a821e31efa4192f372ce883e74ae044fe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwikimedia.org%2Fapi%2Frest_v1%2Fmedia%2Fmath%2Frender%2Fsvg%2F6b9faf0a821e31efa4192f372ce883e74ae044fe&h=55d84aed&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n淨係睇唔撚駛你計都知道麻鳩煩啦！唔好興奮住，我都仲未講要用羅馬數目字；係啊，希臘化時代羅馬打嬴迦太基之後，大半個歐洲都係用羅馬數目字架啦。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ai2-s2-public.s3.amazonaws.com/figures/2017-08-08/297dfdff0c675221fcedaed28fcd3480177af80f/4-Table1-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fai2-s2-public.s3.amazonaws.com%2Ffigures%2F2017-08-08%2F297dfdff0c675221fcedaed28fcd3480177af80f%2F4-Table1-1.png&h=a6abaa58&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n假如教育局下令小學用羅馬數目字同六十進制教學，唔撚駛小三TSA，我保證背完九因歌啲小學雞就要相約跳樓啦。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/statue-mathematician-fibonacci-pisa-old-cemetery-called-camposanto-piazza-dei-miracoli-italy-lived-middle-ages-39589443.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.dreamstime.com%2Fb%2Fstatue-mathematician-fibonacci-pisa-old-cemetery-called-camposanto-piazza-dei-miracoli-italy-lived-middle-ages-39589443.jpg&h=ba15c9a3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n所以話中世紀嘅數字制度改革係幾咁重要，都係多得斐波那契(上圖)呢條契弟，唔係佢香港可以成為國際金融中心？！冇咗佢奠立會計制度，你班會計撚有得撈？冇咗佢記載斐波那契系數，你班炒股撚炒得咁過癮？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://pic.jiaren.org/wp-pic/2014/11/1101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.jiaren.org%2Fwp-pic%2F2014%2F11%2F1101.jpg&h=2e65d378&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n既然創業撚都要拜馬雲，咁會計撚、炒股撚、家教撚點講都要拜拜斐波那契啦啩！<br />\n依家我正式宣佈，全城膜拜斐波那契，佢嘅生日立法通過成為公眾假期。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">支持請正皮，下一篇會講十字軍東征再加商人治港嘅城邦。</span>"},{"pid":"6d564de61eceb7af15b15b9b12ecb07245a63078","tid":712606,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:19:04.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9911165cae6de83d56f1c1dbf06adbd2bbb1d8fc","tid":712606,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"生性啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00bb568ce7c0c64dda3165d363f49e42f2c47db","tid":712606,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:51:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收皮啦大陸狗</span>"},{"pid":"3fc7d8ba91a12e2ea84eb1236f58f59668a5c8cc","tid":712606,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:54:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收皮啦大陸狗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/165317_3c5d525ac55b7521b6d20238c67749c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F165317_3c5d525ac55b7521b6d20238c67749c4.png&h=38f91759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/165317_19cc0bd5da61ae899669ade3ddb5e351.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F165317_19cc0bd5da61ae899669ade3ddb5e351.png&h=0b79d423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/699719/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/699719/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7c6753114869b3db472167acbd425556c982e9d9","tid":712606,"uid":187216,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T09:03:58.000Z","msg":"多謝樓上巴打咁積極幫我推po, 我敬你嘅：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jiuwa.net/tuku/20170712/eS78RbQe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiuwa.net%2Ftuku%2F20170712%2FeS78RbQe.jpg&h=17c12df6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}